Lustre文件系统	MGS
management,system architecture
MGS是Lustre文件系统的重要组成部分，负责管理元数据目标(MGT)。

Lustre文件系统	MDS
8,metadata management,system architecture
MDS是Lustre文件系统的组件之一，负责处理元数据操作。<SEP>The Lustre file system uses MDS to manage metadata operations, such as file creation and access control."|>"metadata management, system architecture

Lustre文件系统	MDT
9,metadata storage,system architecture
MDT是Lustre文件系统中存储元数据的组件，主MDT保存根目录。<SEP>The Lustre file system relies on MDTs to manage metadata, including file attributes and directory structures."|>"metadata management, file system architecture

Lustre文件系统	OSS
8,data storage,system architecture
OSS为OST提供I/O服务，是Lustre文件系统的关键组件。<SEP>The Lustre file system uses OSS to manage data storage on OSTs, providing I/O services for clients."|>"data management, storage services

Lustre文件系统	OST
9,data storage,system architecture
OST是Lustre文件系统中存储文件数据的组件。<SEP>The Lustre file system uses OSTs to store actual file data, enabling scalable and parallel data access across multiple storage targets."|>"data storage, scalability

LNet	Lustre文件系统
8,communication,network infrastructure
LNet is the networking layer that enables communication between components of the Lustre file system."|>"networking, system architecture<SEP>LNet是Lustre文件系统的网络通信基础设施，负责节点间的数据传输。

FID用于唯一标识Lustre文件系统中的文件，是文件管理的重要机制。

LFSCK	Lustre文件系统
7,8,data integrity,recovery
LFSCK is a tool used by the Lustre file system to check and repair inconsistencies between MDT and OST components."|>"system maintenance, data integrity<SEP>LFSCK is a tool used to ensure the consistency of the Lustre file system, particularly between MDTs and OSTs."|>"system maintenance, data integrity<SEP>LFSCK是Lustre文件系统的灾难恢复工具，用于检查和修复文件系统一致性。

Lustre文件系统	NFS
file sharing,protocol compatibility,protocol integration
Lustre可通过NFS协议导出文件系统，使其兼容非Linux客户端。<SEP>NFS是Lustre文件系统支持的导出协议之一，用于共享文件。

CIFS	Lustre文件系统
file sharing,protocol compatibility,protocol integration
